function Start()
-- Disable traversal in the battlefield
SetTraversalEnabled(Battlefield_Traversal, false)

-- Set Battlefield Bridge to be Invulnerable
	for i, idBridge in ipairs( Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Breaking_Bridge")) do 
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idBridge, true)
		
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation("QST_Hell_Prava", Donan_at_Bridge)

Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Lorath_at_Bridge, false)
Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Lorath_at_Bridge, Lorath_Prava, "NPC_Run", true)
Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(Lorath_at_Bridge, Lorath_Prava)
	
Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Donan_at_Bridge, false)
Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Donan_at_Bridge, Donan_Prava, "NPC_Run", true)
Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(Donan_at_Bridge, Donan_Prava)
				
Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, false)
Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, Neyrelle_Prava, "NPC_Run", true)
Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, Neyrelle_Prava)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

followerDonan = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Donan_Follower_Horadrim")
followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerDonan) == true then
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation("QST_Hell_Dead_Knights", followerDonan)
	end

end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)

-- Disable monster spawners in ambush
for i, idBridgeSpawners in ipairs( Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Bridge_Spawners")) do 
		Hydra.ActorDisable(idBridgeSpawners, true)
		end

end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

-- Neyrelle interrupts the dispelling ritual
Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_1hand_horadric")
Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(Neyrelle_at_Bridge)

end

function Start()

-- Neyrelle starts casting the spell 

Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "NPC_Neyrelle_Attk_Cast_Runes")
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_1hand_horadric", true)
Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(Conv_Firewall_Chant_1, Neyrelle_at_Bridge)

-- Enable fallen spawners after few seconds delay
Hydra.Wait(3)
	for i, idBridgeSpawners in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Bridge_Spawners")) do 
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idBridgeSpawners, true)
			
	end

end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)

-- Spawn shaman miniboss and lunatics
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateInActorGroup("QST_Hell_Bridge_Spawners_Boss")

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

-- Donan comments on the attack
Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(Conv_Bridge_Attack, Donan_at_Bridge)

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	for i, idBattlefieldSpawners in ipairs( Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Battlefield_Spawners")) do 
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idBattlefieldSpawners, false)
	end

	Hydra.EventSend("Exit Stage")

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
followerDonan = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Donan_Follower_Horadrim")
followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_OneArmed")


-- Lorath follower runs to his static place
				Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerLorath)
				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerLorath, false)
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerLorath, Lorath_at_Bridge, "NPC_Run", true)
				Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerLorath, Lorath_at_Bridge)
				
-- Donan follower runs to his static place		
				Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerDonan)
				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerDonan, false)
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerDonan, Donan_at_Bridge, "NPC_Run", true)
				Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerDonan, Donan_at_Bridge)
				
-- Neyrelle follower runs to her static place
				Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
				-- Neyrelle comments on the barrier
						Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(Conv_Bridge_Callout, followerNeyrelle)
				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "NPC_Run", true)
				Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
				
				Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerDonan)
				Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerLorath)
				Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
				
-- Event sent to progress the quest

				Hydra.QActorEventSend(followerNeyrelle, "BarrierFound")

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

-- Neyrelle walks up to the soulstone and loots it
Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Neyrelle_Prava, Loc_Neyrelle_Soulstone, "NPC_Walk", true)
Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(Neyrelle_Prava, Loc_Neyrelle_Soulstone)
Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimOneShot(Neyrelle_Prava, sAnimCrouch)
Hydra.Wait(4)
-- Disable soulstone (Neyrelle loots it)
Hydra.ActorDisable(Actor_Soulstone)
Hydra.QActorEventSend(Neyrelle_Prava, "Soulstone_Looted")

--Hydra.GizmoPlayAnim(idActorGizmo, "AnimKey_Open", true)



end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

Hydra.ActorEnable(Prava_Imprisoned)
--Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(Gizmo_Knight_Soulstone, "AnimKey_Open")
--Hydra.GizmoPlayAnim(Gizmo_Knight_Soulstone, "AnimKey_Open", true)
Hydra.ActorDelete(Gizmo_Knight_Soulstone)

Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(Prava_Imprisoned, "NPC_Prava_Wounded_Campaign")

-- Adjust Neyrelle to look at Prava (Donan and Lorath are already looking at her)
Hydra.QActorFaceActor(Neyrelle_Prava, Prava_Imprisoned)


--Prava crawls from under the mega demon body (crawl -> kneel)
--Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(Prava_Imprisoned, "AnimKey_OnChest_Kneel", "AnimKey_Kneel_Idle")
--Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(Prava_Imprisoned)

-- 

end

function Start(szGroup)

-- Neyrelle attempts to dispell the firewall again

				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, false)
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, Loc_Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "NPC_Run", true)
				Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, Loc_Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
				Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
				Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "NPC_Neyrelle_Attk_Cast_Runes")
				Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_1hand_horadric", true)
				Hydra.Wait(3)
				Hydra.QActorEventSend(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "BridgeCleared")
				
				
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

-- Neyrelle finishes dispelling the firewall

Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(Conv_Firewall_Chant_2, Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, Conv_Firewall_Chant_2)
Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(Neyrelle_at_Bridge)
Hydra.QActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(Neyrelle_at_Bridge, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_1hand_horadric")
Hydra.QActorEventSend(Neyrelle_at_Bridge,"FirewallDispelled")

end
